 Death looked at the bot. "Thats fine I will wait"
 He pulled out his reaper and broke into its two even
halves. Sticking both ends on parralel to each other.
He made it deep enough to support his weight and sat
down on them. He pulled out a magazine from his back
plate. The name of it was assasins of today. He
started flipping through the pages patiently.
